{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act3d0_level_act3d0_04_end","storyGroup":"act3d0","storySort":11,"storyDependence":"act3d0_level_act3d0_04_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"OF-4","storyName":"他是将军","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"赫拉格指出，黑的身份恐怕不只是市长保镖这么简单，而这番猜测被锡兰听到。\n锡兰不禁对自己的家人产生了动摇。\n\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act3d0/level_act3d0_04_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"a003_04","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":9,"next":11,"characters":["赫拉格","锡兰"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第六关（后）","id":0},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_bg_bg_hotel.png","fadetime":"1","id":1},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","id":2,"musicid":0},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"character","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","id":6},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"这个菲林族女性并非泛泛之辈。","id":7,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"9","text":"这还是难不倒你的。"},"2":{"id":"9","text":"将军，没受伤吧？"}},"values":[],"id":8},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"不必担心。她的部下都只是些庸人。你们安全之后，撤退对我来说还算轻松。","id":10,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"只不过，关于这个保镖的身份，我有些猜测。","id":11,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"13","text":"身份"},"2":{"id":"13","text":"难道说......"}},"values":[],"id":12},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"哥伦比亚，菲林族，女性，银发、金瞳、黑弩。是杀手，也是佣兵。","id":14,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"杀手闻名于诸城是件可耻的事，但这些传闻实在是过于有名。","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"譬如说，毁掉一整个哥伦比亚家族。一个强盛的家族，重要人物在数年内陆续暴毙，逐渐走向衰落，最终彻底被除名。","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"再如，猎杀一整支巡逻队。这支巡逻队在哥伦比亚边境烧杀抢掠，自诩野蛮人的征服者，不断地向异族施加暴行和惨剧。","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"之后的一个月内，他们在山间逃窜，不断死去，最后只剩下一个残废回到城市胡言乱语。","id":18,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"以及向我叙说故事的人的遭遇。","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"21","text":"又发生了什么？"},"2":{"id":"21","text":"请说吧，我不害怕。"}},"values":[],"id":20},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"不必多说了。他的伤疤从左肩延伸到右脚后跟。","id":22,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"杀人如麻的家伙比比皆是，我也如此。","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"当然，这个杀手失踪已久。","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"只是，如果她就是那个人，那么摆在我们面前的，自然是腥风血雨。","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"27","text":"水比想象中的深。"},"2":{"id":"27","text":"锡兰被蒙在鼓里？"}},"values":[],"id":26},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"也许市长并非不知情。","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"不如说，如果她是市长的杀手，我不会感到奇怪。","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":30},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"3","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":31},{"type":"text","text":"（玻璃杯粉碎）","id":32},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"34","text":"锡兰？！"},"2":{"id":"34","text":"你从什么时候......"}},"values":[],"id":33},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":34,"end":58},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"锡兰小姐，你不用躲着偷听。","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_348_ceylon_4#8","focus":"2","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我，我想给你们倒杯水......","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/89/Avg_char_348_ceylon_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"赫拉格爷爷，那个佣兵，是从什么时候开始活动，又是在什么时候失踪的？","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/89/Avg_char_348_ceylon_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_348_ceylon_4#8","focus":"1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"她的事迹开始闻名，甚至在我还未退伍之时。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"而她销声匿迹则是一年之前，随着那个家族的覆灭一起。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_348_ceylon_4#8","focus":"2","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"......直到六年前，黑都在维多利亚照顾我的生活。","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/89/Avg_char_348_ceylon_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"但是有一天，她忽然说爸爸需要她回去做事，就走了，只在每年圣诞节的时候来接我回家。","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/89/Avg_char_348_ceylon_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_348_ceylon_4#3","focus":"2","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"但、但是，她刚才只是态度不好，而且听了别人的命令，黑她怎么可能是那种杀人如麻的杀手！","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_char_348_ceylon_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"而且，按照你们的说法，你们想说克洛宁的背后是我爸爸在授意吗？！","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_char_348_ceylon_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我不信！","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_char_348_ceylon_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_348_ceylon_4#3","focus":"1","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"我不作推测。但我也说过，即使是最信任的人，也未必对你毫无保留。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"信与不信，我不关心。只是，她身上的乌萨斯制式武器留下的伤痕，我绝不会看错。这支队伍被埋葬在大雪中。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"现状如你所见，博士。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"如果火山的情报处理也有市政府参与，那么这件事我们未必应该插手。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"锡兰小姐，你也应该看清事实。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#9","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我......我需要冷静一下。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_348_ceylon_9.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":59},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":60},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorclosequite","volume":"0.9","id":61},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":62},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"博士，请。","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"66","text":"啊？"},"2":{"id":"66","text":"我是该做些什么吧？"}},"values":[],"id":65},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":66,"end":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"自然。现在她需要一个能够理解她的人。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":68,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":69},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":70},{"type":"image","id":71}],"characters":["赫拉格","锡兰"]}